data.meta_description: Apr 19, 2017 - Princess Alexandra (Alexandra Caroline Marie Charlotte Louise Julia) (1 Dec 1844–20 Nov 1925) Wife of King Edward VII (Albert Edward) (9 Nov 1841–6 May 1910) UK. Child of King Christian IX (8 Apr 1818–29 Jan 1906) Denmark (from Schleswig-Holstein-Sonderburg-Glücksburg, Germany) & Princess Louise (Louise Wilhelmine Frederikke Caroline Auguste Julie) (7 Sep 1817–29 Sep 1898) Hesse, Germany. . See more ideas about princess alexandra, queen alexandra, alexandra of denmark.
